description: Hiroki Endo’s critically acclaimed manga series returns with a massive volume packed with brutal battles, strange sci-fi surprises, political intrigue, and an expanding “intelligent virus” that’s taking over the world! As Elijah searches Australia for his missing sister, the Propater organization sends several rounds of cyborg assassins afterhim! The “Maya” virus grows and threatens to absorb all human life into it, Elijah is reunited with a few talented friends, and a budding romance restores a bit of hope to this violent, postapocalyptic near future!
name: Vol. 13
